    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to depictions with a point of view from the side of the subject, as contrasted to depictions taken from the back or front. For views of figures taken from the side, use "profiles."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a representaciones con un punto de vista desde el lado del sujeto, en contraste a representaciones tomadas del lado posterior o del frente. Para vistas de figuras tomadas de lado, use "perfil."
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar afbeeldingen met een gezichtspunt vanuit de zijkant van het onderwerp, in tegenstelling tot afbeeldingen die van voren of van achteren zijn genomen. Gebruik 'profielen' voor figuren die vanaf de zijkant worden gezien.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refere-se às representações com ponto de vista das laterais do tema, em contraste às representações feitas da parte frontal ou posterior. Para vistas de figuras realizadas de lado, use "perfis".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
